### Private schools

Beyond the public system, the [Archdiocese of Miami](/Archdiocese_of_Miami) plays a role in the educational offerings, operating area Catholic schools. [Monsignor Edward Pace High School](/Monsignor_Edward_Pace_High_School) is situated directly within the city limits of Miami Gardens, providing an alternative to the public system. Historically, the archdiocese also managed Saint Monica School in Miami Gardens, though its operations have since ceased.

