### Public libraries

The intellectual needs of the community are served by the [Miami-Dade Public Library System](/Miami-Dade_Public_Library_System), which operates the North Dade Regional Library. This facility first opened its doors to the public in September 1979, offering a quiet refuge for knowledge and contemplation amidst the bustling city.

